P4i&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\\\" role=\\\"link\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"cursor: pointer; outline: none; list-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; touch-action: manipulation; text-align: inherit; display: inline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit;\\\">#hybryda<\\/a><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Historic&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\"> + <\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Historic&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\"><a class=\\\"oajrlxb2 g5ia77u1 qu0x051f esr5mh6w e9989ue4 r7d6kgcz rq0escxv nhd2j8a9 nc684nl6 p7hjln8o kvgmc6g5 cxmmr5t8 oygrvhab hcukyx3x jb3vyjys rz4wbd8a qt6c0cv9 a8nywdso i1ao9s8h esuyzwwr f1sip0of lzcic4wl gpro0wi8 q66pz984 b1v8xokw\\\" href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.facebook.com\\/hashtag\\/lpg?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZXj10ERtYFVazgGhPt6oqInvR_Si7470dptxO8sM9Y6zZkUix6S0O1kj-9KYl_2EzM_u9w4hDrnRbbzaQK-OmlXTHeCdFkyGvRwXSfMMf_zHvxziUZ2MOSFsMSGBDDymyP-o0PhnXTxKThYnh4OLP4i&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\\\" role=\\\"link\\\" tabindex=\\\"0\\\" style=\\\"cursor: pointer; outline: none; list-style: none; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; touch-action: manipulation; text-align: inherit; display: inline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: inherit;\\\">#LPG<\\/a><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Segoe UI Historic&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; white-space: pre-wrap;\\\"> portfolio is joined by the \\\"fresh\\\" Suzuki Swatch 1.8 hybrid from 2021, in which the installation was installed by the AUTO-SERVICE workshop <\\/span><span class=\\\"pq6dq46d tbxw36s4 knj5qynh kvgmc6g5 ditlmg2l oygrvhab nvdbi5me sf5mxxl7 gl3lb2sf hhz5lgdu\\\" style=\\\"margin: 0px 1px; height: 16px; width: 1